  "name": "Non-cannulated F1717 compression-bending credibility assessment — COU1",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. COU1 is the validation activity itself — the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Validation evidence is drawn from a prospective observational registry of bench-test records compiled across two independent laboratories, providing rich QoI coverage for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement.",
